  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t中国共匪阿谀奉迎舔吮俯仰光速争抢，奴才 “<b>睐性瓶儿</b>” 速舔主子习近瓶儿 养猪白酒粪便处理 “<b>新质生产力</b>” 登峰造极勇攀宇宙蚂蚁蟑螂灭虫老鼠消炎液肺炎病毒研发散播高峰。从此中国大陆人体痔疮鸡眼脚气红白狼疮藓疥羊角疯癫痫肺气肿胰腺炎乳腺癌一概跑步融入 <b>新质生产力</b> 研发浪潮顺手捞出负数纳米级别饼干锌片等等…。<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS95T2JWV0VTLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/yObVWES.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/yObVWES.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yObVWES.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n后人喟叹曰：<br/>\n<b>人家思维拚智能</b><br/>\n<b>A I软 硬 聪明赢</b><br/>\n<b>土匪阿谀马屁猛</b><br/>\n<b>东施效颦巨婴鸣</b>。<br/>\n<br/>\n<b><a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/38242\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/38242\">乱世笑林</a></b><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS8xRkx4d01YLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/1FLxwMX.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/1FLxwMX.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1FLxwMX.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
